But I use that as fire beneath me.

1559
01:01:55.560 --> 01:01:58.320
And I'm going to use that fire to win this
veto.

1560
01:01:58.940 --> 01:02:01.980
Dee definitely made a mistake putting me
on the block.

1561
01:02:02.410 --> 01:02:05.700
I was one of the pivotal people that
helped her solve that puzzle.

1562
01:02:05.920 --> 01:02:07.580
I am not scared of competition.

1563
01:02:08.320 --> 01:02:11.740
You give me two chances with the veto and
the blockbuster.

1564
01:02:12.090 --> 01:02:14.540
To bet on myself and get my ass off that
block.

1565
01:02:14.541 --> 01:02:15.960
I'm going to do it.

1566
01:02:16.215 --> 01:02:17.540
So I know now.

1567
01:02:17.920 --> 01:02:20.080
No more all smiles and having fun.

1568
01:02:20.240 --> 01:02:24.160
I'm fired up and I'm going to go in there
and get my ass off that block.

1569
01:02:25.210 --> 01:02:28.280
So everything has gone exactly according
to plan.

1570
01:02:28.500 --> 01:02:34.980
Dee and the crossover alliance wanted to
put up Yash and Mallory and Taylor.

1571
01:02:35.295 --> 01:02:37.560
Dee did what she said she was going to do.

1572
01:02:38.135 --> 01:02:40.380
This is a beautiful start to season 28.

1573
01:02:40.680 --> 01:02:43.040
Who will win the power of veto?

1574
01:02:44.540 --> 01:02:48.840
Who will choose to save either Taylor.
Yash or Mallory from the chopping block?

1575
01:02:49.390 --> 01:02:54.320
Find out Wednesday night at 8.
7 central on Big Brother.
